29
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,960
Why rush off?

30
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,670
Why not stay here with your sister?

31
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:07,210
There's more fun to come.

32
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:08,690
It'd be a pity to miss it.

33
00:02:08,690 --> 00:02:10,010
A feast, huh?

34
00:02:10,010 --> 00:02:12,810
Stop spouting nonsense.

35
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,940
My brother's just straightforward.

36
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:19,280
Let's meet another day.

37
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:24,080
Back so soon?

38
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:27,800
I thought you'd be busy out there for days.

39
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:31,130
What, don't want to see me?

40
00:02:31,770 --> 00:02:33,720
No way.

41
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:46,080
Do you like it here?

42
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,240
It's okay.

43
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:50,490
The food's better than at the academy.

44
00:02:50,490 --> 00:02:52,290
Shame I was too busy entertaining them.

45
00:02:52,290 --> 00:02:54,420
Didn't get to enjoy it.

46
00:02:58,270 --> 00:03:02,930
With your cultivation now, you don't need this food.

47
00:03:02,930 --> 00:03:07,220
Other than filling your stomach, it's useless.

48
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:10,650
I eat simply because I'm greedy.

49
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:18,130
I really can't understand the pleasure of indulging in food.

50
00:03:21,170 --> 00:03:26,270
If someone can't sleep well or savor good food,

51
00:03:26,270 --> 00:03:29,250
their life must lose a lot of joy.

52
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:33,140
I suggest you try more good food.

53
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:36,230
It really helps keep you happy.

54
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:42,020
Where are we going?

55
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:46,090
So, you brought me here for a private feast!

56
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:49,440
Those people never stop talking.

57
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:53,010
And you barely ate either, right?

58
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:55,290
You know me too well!

59
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:56,590
I'll eat...

60
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:58,100
Go on, eat.

61
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:08,540
The custard's silky smooth,
and melts in your mouth.

62
00:04:08,540 --> 00:04:13,860
That faint touch of mushroom brings the flavor to its peak.

63
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:17,000
A taste so divine!

64
00:04:20,220 --> 00:04:21,560
What's with you?

65
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:24,580
You've got food in front of you, yet you insist on taking mine.

66
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:26,700
I take whatever I want.

67
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:47,760
Crisp and springy!

68
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:15,490
What's so great about this stuff?

69
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:16,980
 Annoying pest. 

70
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:20,130
 I'd love to dump the whole plate on his head! 

71
00:05:25,590 --> 00:05:27,330
You heard that?

72
00:05:29,490 --> 00:05:31,270
Heard what?

73
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,390
Sima Jiao, tell me the truth.

74
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:40,650
Can you hear what I'm thinking?

75
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:45,400
Say something.

76
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:49,600
You can hear my thoughts, can't you?

77
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,440
Liar!

78
00:05:57,440 --> 00:06:00,200
Didn't you say you can't read minds?

79
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,740
I really can't.

80
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:12,580
But lately, when your emotions run wild,

81
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:15,900
I sometimes hear what's on your mind.

82
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:20,570
Only yours.

83
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:24,680
No need to be that precise.

84
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,540
Why just mine?

85
00:06:26,540 --> 00:06:29,340
Abilities shift with circumstances.

86
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:31,880
It's common in the cultivation world.

87
00:06:34,710 --> 00:06:37,060
Any changes with you?

88
00:06:40,610 --> 00:06:46,330
 Don't tell me... it's because of our soul bond. 

89
00:06:46,330 --> 00:06:49,310
 So, even without the Truth Spell, you can hear my heart? 

90
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:54,650
Didn't the teacher explain this
back at the academy?

91
00:06:54,650 --> 00:06:57,680
 Oh, Liao Ting Yan... 

92
00:06:57,680 --> 00:07:02,030
 Better pay attention in those cultivation health classes. 

93
00:07:09,540 --> 00:07:11,860
All those thoughts of yours...

94
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:14,100
I can hear them all.

95
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:19,250
One times one is two...

96
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:22,830
Grandmaster, do you catch every thought

97
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:26,820
in my head when I get worked up?

98
00:07:27,590 --> 00:07:29,690
Not word for word that clear.

99
00:07:29,690 --> 00:07:35,840
But if you start cursing someone, I'll know.

100
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:39,000
So, I'd suggest you stay calm.

101
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,640
 You've got some nerve saying that! 

102
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,170
 You're the one who keeps losing your temper... 

103
00:07:43,170 --> 00:07:44,460
 Four times four is sixteen. 

104
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:46,840
 Five times five is twenty-five... 

105
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:50,610
All you ever think about
is eating and sleeping.

106
00:07:50,610 --> 00:07:55,060
Anything else you're afraid I'll find out?

107
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:58,440
Seems you don't really know me that well.

108
00:07:58,440 --> 00:08:02,150
Where I come from, info's exploding everywhere.

109
00:08:02,150 --> 00:08:04,520
All kinds of crazy things exist.

110
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:07,490
Way beyond what you can imagine.

111
00:08:07,490 --> 00:08:10,500
I'd better recite the times table
to clear my head.

112
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:27,710
No more thinking...

113
00:08:34,230 --> 00:08:37,160
Never seen anyone like this.

114
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:41,910
No wonder you're from the Demon Realm.

115
00:08:42,610 --> 00:08:44,400
Really eye-opening.

116
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:48,040
Please stop peeking into my mind!

117
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:54,410
 Forget it. 

118
00:08:54,410 --> 00:08:58,320
 From today, I'll be calm and peaceful. 

119
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:03,240
 Thinking back, ever since this soul bond, I've cursed him plenty in my head. 

120
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:05,830
 Did he hear it all? 

121
00:09:05,830 --> 00:09:07,510
Yes.

122
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:13,950
Grandmaster, please quit speaking directly to my mind.

123
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,810
 Wait... 

124
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:24,830
 I cursed Sima Jiao like crazy before, yet he never reacted. 

125
00:09:24,830 --> 00:09:28,100
 No anger, no killing me. 

126
00:09:28,100 --> 00:09:31,590
 Could it be true love? 

127
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,350
Didn't he hear it?

128
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:39,570
Did you really not hear it?

129
00:09:49,990 --> 00:09:54,120
I'm resting now. Do as you please.

130
00:10:07,230 --> 00:10:11,040
Stay calm. Don't stir trouble.

131
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:14,940
I'm already staying calm.

132
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:19,900
Go rest in your own bed!

133
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,180
My bed...

134
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:25,560
