155
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:58,220
Sir, what about cultivation partners?

156
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:01,350
Quiet!

157
00:12:01,350 --> 00:12:06,880
Even cultivation partners don't easily enter each other's soul manor.

158
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:10,350
It's extremely dangerous.

159
00:12:10,350 --> 00:12:15,630
If you're truly fortunate to find a partner

160
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:20,510
who shares life and death with you,
you may attempt it.

161
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:24,860
But you're still young, unaware of the dangers.

162
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:31,460
Don't chase a moment's pleasure
and lose what matters.

163
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:36,750
 Feels like Sima Jiao and I are problem students sneaking forbidden fruit. 

164
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:39,920
Soul bond is the most intimate bond.

165
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:46,090
If one dies, the other often can't survive.

166
00:12:46,090 --> 00:12:51,600
Because the souls are bound too tightly,

167
00:12:53,990 --> 00:13:00,170
the feelings too deep to cut apart.

168
00:13:00,170 --> 00:13:06,300
So, never take this lightly.

169
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:12,110
 We haven't even started dating, and it's straight to life-and-death vows? 

170
00:13:12,110 --> 00:13:15,860
 Is it still time for Sima Jiao and me to switch to separate beds? 

171
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:19,750
 No, wait. It's one thing if I didn't know. 

172
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:22,470
 But how could Sima Jiao not know? 

173
00:13:22,470 --> 00:13:28,160
 Could it be...
he's already seen me as his other half? 

174
00:13:39,430 --> 00:13:43,490
Ting Yan. I won't be here tonight.

175
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:47,060
Then be careful out there.

176
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:50,220
Want me to bring you something?

177
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,350
Why ask like that?

178
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:54,800
I'm heading out.

179
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:57,340
If you want anything, I'll bring it back.

180
00:13:57,340 --> 00:14:03,040
 Coming home with gifts
sounds just like a married couple. 

181
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:05,470
Anything's fine. I'm not picky.

182
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:08,710
All right, wait for me.

183
00:14:08,710 --> 00:14:11,100
I won't keep you waiting long.

184
00:14:15,990 --> 00:14:19,040
Why's he being so gentle?

185
00:14:21,590 --> 00:14:25,430
Is he really taking me
as his cultivation partner?

186
00:14:40,710 --> 00:14:42,630
Sect Master Shi, why summon me?

187
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:44,820
Have you tracked down Sima Jiao?

188
00:14:44,820 --> 00:14:48,130
Madam Ye. Please, sit.

189
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:59,830
Lately, my clan has faced repeated attacks.

190
00:14:59,830 --> 00:15:02,440
I sent people to investigate.

191
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:07,280
However, we found no clues linked to Sima Jiao.

192
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:12,280
So, could you help look into this?

193
00:15:12,280 --> 00:15:15,660
No need to beat around the bush.

194
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:21,800
Right outside your hall,

195
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:27,060
my disciple found something interesting.

196
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:29,380
A scale from Nian Jiu!

197
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:37,250
So, you set spies on me.

198
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:40,700
How is that spying? We're allies.

199
00:15:40,700 --> 00:15:43,300
Allies should care for one another.

200
00:15:43,300 --> 00:15:48,510
But it seems this ally of mine is keeping secrets.

201
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:50,800
The black serpent is indeed in my hall.

202
00:15:50,800 --> 00:15:54,980
But he knows nothing
of Sima Jiao's whereabouts.

203
00:15:54,980 --> 00:15:56,160
Truly nothing?

204
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:57,660
Yes.

205
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,400
But is he honest with you or not?

206
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:05,470
We can test and see.

207
00:16:05,470 --> 00:16:10,100
He's the only being
who stays by Sima Jiao's side.

208
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:16,280
So, tell me, if this black serpent is in danger,

209
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:20,200
won't Sima Jiao step in to save him?

210
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:22,710
You want me to harm the serpent?

211
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,910
You can't bear to?

212
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,340
You're back.

213
00:17:01,340 --> 00:17:03,190
I'm back.

214
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:10,080
What's that in your hands?

215
00:17:10,080 --> 00:17:15,070
Well... I found it in a treasure vault.

216
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:17,930
It looked good, so I brought it back for you.

217
00:17:17,930 --> 00:17:20,640
This isn't just an ordinary mirror, is it?

218
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:22,440
How do you use it?

219
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:25,960
If you infuse it with spiritual power,

220
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:31,000
the two mirrors can reflect each other even from thousands of miles away.

221
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:37,740
Shame the resolution
isn't as clear as a cell phone.

222
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:39,310
What?

223
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:43,170
Nothing. I like it.

224
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:51,920
Liar. If you don't like it, I'll break it.

225
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:53,510
What are you doing? I said I like it!

226
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:54,560
Give it back.

227
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:57,310
You went out of your way to bring me this gift.

228
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:59,710
So, hand it over!

229
00:17:59,710 --> 00:18:05,230
Then how are you going to thank me?

230
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:28,480
 ♫ Snow not gone, flame not out ♫ 

231
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:32,080
 ♫ Prism of three lifetimes ♫ 

232
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:37,820
 ♫ You, untouched by moon's regrets ♫ 

233
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:43,730
Is this your thank-you gift?

234
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:47,810
Let me be clear...

235
00:18:49,270 --> 00:18:51,810
This is not thanks.

236
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:58,440
From now on,
you'll be more than just my boyfriend.

