247
00:20:15,580 --> 00:20:19,180
 ♫ No one reaches, no one hears ♫ 

248
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:22,960
 ♫ Thousands of stars in your eyes ♫ 

249
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:28,325
