Liao Ting Yan, stop it!

263
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:43,090
So, even this short-tempered Grandmaster can be as soft as a kitten.

264
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:10,290
Hey, my mirror!

265
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:17,920
If only there are more of these mirrors.

266
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:22,610
We can place them everywhere, and gather all the images onto one.

267
00:22:22,610 --> 00:22:24,690
That will be live streaming!

268
00:22:25,710 --> 00:22:27,420
Live streaming?

269
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:31,050
What's...

270
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:33,400
live streaming?

271
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:36,960
It means you can watch
everything happening in real time.

272
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:42,160
For example, put a mirror in the square of Gengchen Celestial Palace,

273
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:45,750
we'll see disciples dueling.

274
00:22:45,750 --> 00:22:51,260
Put one in a busy marketplace, we'll see the bustle of mortal life.

275
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:55,740
Even in the forests and mountains, among flowers and trees,

276
00:22:55,740 --> 00:22:59,200
we'll get a nature documentary.

277
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:01,300
Won't that be wonderful?

278
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:05,620
Sounds pretty good.

279
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:11,070
From now on, if you hear a sound from it,

280
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:14,620
just channel spiritual power
and tap the mirror.

281
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:18,690
Then I'll see whatever I want?

282
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:46,360
Today, I'll discuss
the Spirit Fire of Fengshan.

283
00:23:46,360 --> 00:23:51,840
Spirit Fire is the foundation
of Gengchen Celestial Palace.

284
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:02,030
The fire nurtures the palace's spiritual veins.

285
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:08,360
Without it, the Celestial Palace lands
will lose all spiritual energy,

286
00:24:08,360 --> 00:24:11,920
turning into a barren waste.

287
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:14,840
Even its fortune will wither.

288
00:24:14,840 --> 00:24:18,680
The Sima clan sustains
the Spirit Fire with their blood.

289
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:21,550
They've safeguarded
the Celestial Palace's prosperity,

290
00:24:21,550 --> 00:24:26,620
and in return gained abilities beyond ordinary cultivators.

291
00:24:26,620 --> 00:24:29,610
Several of them even ascended to godhood...

292
00:24:29,610 --> 00:24:30,970
Sima Jiao!

293
00:24:30,970 --> 00:24:32,620
It's me.

294
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:36,000
Why that look?

295
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:39,780
I just never thought
I'd be using video calls here.

296
00:24:39,780 --> 00:24:42,130
Video...

297
00:24:42,130 --> 00:24:43,990
What's a video call?

298
00:24:43,990 --> 00:24:49,880
It's when we're in different places, but can still see each other
and hear each other talk.

299
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:52,630
So, the Demon Realm
also has Transvision Mirrors?

300
00:24:54,210 --> 00:24:55,450
You can say that.

301
00:24:55,450 --> 00:24:57,600
But we don't call it Transvision Mirror.

302
00:24:57,600 --> 00:24:59,680
We call it a cell phone.

303
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,200
You're amazing.

304
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:04,800
I casually mentioned live streaming, and you made it real.

305
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:09,740
With this mirror, I can remind you...

306
00:25:10,990 --> 00:25:13,490
I'm always there for you.

307
00:25:15,230 --> 00:25:18,120
If you want me to miss you, just say so.

308
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:20,850
No need to dress it up like that.

309
00:25:21,370 --> 00:25:22,930
Forget Sima Jiao.

310
00:25:22,930 --> 00:25:25,560
You're more like Sima Proud-Heart.

311
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:34,600
You said you wanted live streaming, so I visited Three Saints Mountain.

312
00:25:35,230 --> 00:25:38,310
Oh, the tower and palaces are being rebuilt!

313
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:43,810
Doesn't your invisibility have a time limit?

314
00:25:43,810 --> 00:25:46,200
Be careful. Don't get caught.

315
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:49,640
Don't worry. I'm hidden by illusions.

316
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,580
I know what I'm doing.

317
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:54,620
Good, then.

318
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:57,200
Hold it higher! Higher!

319
00:25:57,200 --> 00:26:00,310
I can't see what's there.

320
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:02,180
Sima Jiao?

321
00:26:09,780 --> 00:26:11,290
Hello?

322
00:26:12,550 --> 00:26:13,790
Hello?

323
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:16,820
Don't tell me the mirror's lost signal.

324
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:22,750
Search here for traces of the Spirit Fire.

325
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:26,000
Report at once if you find anything.

326
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:29,880
Hello?

327
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:32,100
Why's the picture frozen?

328
00:26:36,710 --> 00:26:40,150
I nearly got caught by the teacher.

329
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:44,120
This place is like that.

330
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:45,970
Nothing alive here.

331
00:26:45,970 --> 00:26:47,500
You're looking for the Spirit Fire?

332
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:48,990
Find anything?

333
00:26:48,990 --> 00:26:50,720
Not yet.

334
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:53,510
Forget about it.

335
00:26:53,510 --> 00:26:57,000
If you like, just enjoy the scenery.

336
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:06,550
 Good thing I was raised on Grandmaster's blood. 

337
00:27:06,550 --> 00:27:08,710
 I know his aura well. 

338
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:12,620
 Maybe I can find him and Ting Yan soon. 

339
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:21,450
Ru Ling?

340
00:27:21,970 --> 00:27:24,240
Ru Ling's calling me.

341
00:27:33,650 --> 00:27:35,380
Ru Ling!

342
00:27:36,780 --> 00:27:38,440
Ru Ling!

343
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:40,880
Ru Ling, why call me back in such a rush?

344
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,470
Did you run into trouble?

345
00:27:42,470 --> 00:27:44,560
Or did someone bully you?

346
00:27:50,740 --> 00:27:53,860
 Nian Jiu, I had no choice. 

347
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:55,640
 Please forgive me. 

348
00:27:55,640 --> 00:28:00,800
Ru Ling, you called me back just for this?

349
00:28:27,650 --> 00:28:29,380
Ru Ling.

350
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:32,920
Why betray Grandmaster?

351
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:36,120
Sima Jiao has killed countless.
He deserves to die.

352
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:39,470
This isn't betrayal. It's justice!

353
00:28:39,470 --> 00:28:43,380
Ru Ling, tell me...

354
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:46,310
Have they deceived you?

355
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,890
Grandmaster is not that kind of man.

356
00:28:47,890 --> 00:28:49,580
Silence!

357
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:56,100
Do you realize I can kill you right here?

358
00:28:58,070 --> 00:29:00,970
I'm just a serpent by nature.

359
00:29:00,970 --> 00:29:04,710
You gave me the chance to take human form.

360
00:29:04,710 --> 00:29:07,480
This life is yours to begin with.

361
00:29:08,550 --> 00:29:10,900
If you want it back today,

362
00:29:11,890 --> 00:29:13,660
then take it.

363
00:29:20,130 --> 00:29:23,830
I know this hurts you.

364
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:28,550
But bear it for now.

365
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:32,220
Word has spread that you're imprisoned.

366
00:29:33,210 --> 00:29:39,100
I'm sure Sima Jiao
will come for you once he knows.

367
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:45,960
There's someone spying on us.

368
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:47,990
Bite me, then use Breath-Sealing.

369
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:50,060
I'll let you escape.

370
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:56,400
Nian Jiu, we were once master and disciple.

371
00:29:56,400 --> 00:30:00,680
Why throw your life away like this?

372
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:21,030
You killed him so easily.

373
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:23,860
Madam Ye, you're so ruthless!

374
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:26,750
You saw it, Sect Master Shi.

375
00:30:26,750 --> 00:30:28,790
This beast caused trouble.

376
00:30:28,790 --> 00:30:31,110
I had no choice but to put him down.

377
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:36,790
But...

378
00:30:38,020 --> 00:30:41,790
we'll have to try another way to get news.

379
00:30:41,790 --> 00:30:43,490
Rest easy.

380
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:47,630
I have my methods.

381
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:51,720
Guards! Drag him out.

382
00:31:17,820 --> 00:31:19,820
Got bullied again?

383
00:31:25,820 --> 00:31:27,440
Grandmaster.

384
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:29,270
Grandmaster!

385
00:31:29,270 --> 00:31:31,400
I was wrong.

386
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:37,440
Grandmaster, in Yin Palace, I learned someone is hunting for your trail.

387
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:41,530
Thankfully Ru Ling helped me slip away.

388
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:53,400
This... It's a tracking spell!

389
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:55,520
I've been tricked!

390
00:31:55,970 --> 00:31:58,230
Why else would Shi Qian Lv let you go?

391
00:31:58,230 --> 00:32:01,960
So, they used me to get to you.

392
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:06,710
Grandmaster, for bringing you such trouble,

393
00:32:06,710 --> 00:32:08,450
I deserve to die.

394
00:32:08,450 --> 00:32:09,550
No more nonsense.

395
00:32:09,550 --> 00:32:11,070
Move.

396
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:20,140
Grandmaster, there's an array!

397
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:32,610
No point hiding.

398
00:32:32,610 --> 00:32:34,290
Show yourself.

399
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:41,730
Forgive us, Grandmaster.

400
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:58,340
Even wounded as I am,

401
00:32:58,990 --> 00:33:01,890
your tricks are far too weak.

402
00:33:13,410 --> 00:33:18,240
Grandmaster! Did you suffer a serious wound before, and still not heal?

403
00:33:25,230 --> 00:33:27,510
Go tell your master this.

404
00:33:27,510 --> 00:33:29,680
"Sima Jiao never fought us."

405
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:33,720
"Once he broke out of the array,
we lost track of him."

406
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:41,130
Why did you let them go?

407
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:46,750
Those puppets can sense
the Sima bloodline within Shi territory

408
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:49,180
and seek out the Spirit Fire.

409
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:52,230
They are also the torches I've chosen.

410
00:33:52,230 --> 00:33:57,480
When the time is right, they will ignite the hidden fire I planted,

411
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:00,760
to complete the final step of my plan.

412
00:34:07,990 --> 00:34:09,840
This must be kept secret from Ye Ru Ling.

413
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:11,180
Understood.

414
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:16,960
How was the tracking spell broken?

415
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,030
It was my failure.

416
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:22,900
I could only watch as Sima Jiao undid both the array and the tracking spell,
then vanished.

417
00:34:25,030 --> 00:34:26,550
And he didn't see you?

418
00:34:26,550 --> 00:34:29,740
No, we kept hidden, never fought him.

419
00:34:32,780 --> 00:34:34,180
I'm off.

420
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:40,230
How did he escape?

421
00:34:41,070 --> 00:34:46,880
Zhen Xu, I sent you to investigate Ri Gui.

422
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:48,530
Any leads?

423
00:34:48,530 --> 00:34:51,260
Nothing suspicious so far.

424
00:34:54,050 --> 00:34:58,400
Now go check if there's a spy among us.

425
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,800
Understood.

426
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:48,470
Too much live streaming gets boring anyway.

427
00:35:48,470 --> 00:35:51,190
Why aren't you back yet?

428
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:02,470
What's going on?

429
00:36:03,140 --> 00:36:06,780
Did I mess up
from learning too many spells lately?

430
00:36:08,180 --> 00:36:11,260
I'll check some books.

431
00:36:14,890 --> 00:36:18,360
What do you want to look up? I can teach you.

432
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:23,650
So, you finally came back.

433
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:33,290
What were you drawing just now?

434
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:36,970
This is called an emoticon.

435
00:36:38,190 --> 00:36:40,510
My personal code.

436
00:36:40,510 --> 00:36:42,170
Cute, huh?

437
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,800
It's so late.

438
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,880
Why aren't you asleep?

439
00:36:58,720 --> 00:37:01,030
What are you so smug about?

440
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:05,070
I wasn't waiting for you.

441
00:37:05,070 --> 00:37:09,150
While you were gone,
I went to classes, I hung out,

442
00:37:09,150 --> 00:37:10,880
and I bought snacks, clothes, furniture.

443
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,610
I was living fine...

444
00:37:37,470 --> 00:37:39,380
Don't worry.

445
00:37:41,240 --> 00:37:43,760
These days won't last much longer.

446
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:49,380
If you're not well,
don't push yourself so hard.

447
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:56,800
No need to worry about me.

448
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:05,880
Tomorrow, I'll stay here a while longer.

449
00:38:36,450 --> 00:38:38,820
You really won't go out?

450
00:38:38,820 --> 00:38:41,550
 Is it to keep me company? 

451
00:38:41,550 --> 00:38:43,670
Do you like crowds?

452
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:48,190
In a few days, it'll be the liveliest time Gengchen Celestial Palace has seen.

453
00:38:48,190 --> 00:38:51,470
Some kind of festival?

454
00:38:51,470 --> 00:38:54,140
 Don't tell me it's a date. 

455
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:57,010
 My heart's already racing. 

456
00:38:57,800 --> 00:38:59,650
Not a festival.

457
00:39:00,690 --> 00:39:05,520
But I'll make it something worth remembering.

458
00:39:08,180 --> 00:39:11,090
Oh, so it's business after all.

459
00:39:11,090 --> 00:39:14,020
 There goes my little heart, crushed. 

460
00:39:18,890 --> 00:39:24,130
Didn't you say only when I'm worked up you can hear my thoughts?

461
00:39:24,130 --> 00:39:27,520
And you think you weren't worked up just now?

462
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,740
What's wrong?

463
00:39:43,740 --> 00:39:45,670
Mad at me?

464
00:39:46,550 --> 00:39:47,620
This person is now asleep.

465
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:49,280
Please leave a message after the beep.

466
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,010
Beep.

467
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:55,800
You laugh way too easily!

468
00:39:55,800 --> 00:40:00,420
You're finally back,
and all you do is tease me.

469
00:40:01,470 --> 00:40:06,300
Then tell me, what do you like most?

